Incident Response > [T3]: Lab - RITA: Generate a report with the findings

Generate a report with the findings

Although the RITA console's output is epic and can be extended if your Linux fu is good, it still provides a simple and to-the-point HTML report that you can use to fiddle with the analyzed data.

To generate the report, all you have to do is execute the following command in your terminal:

rita html-report octopus
